### Example 3: Create service without specific countries (global service)
POST {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/services
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Desarrollo Backend .NET",
  "hourlyRate": 50.00,
  "description": "Desarrollo de APIs REST con .NET Core, implementación de arquitectura limpia y patrones de diseño.",
  "providerId": "5B92770C-0815-4CB0-8FFD-1F7F7D44BACA",
  "countryCodes": []
}

